  "name": "RPlog_Fleming_Interrogates_Sandor",
  "title": "Fleming Interrogates Sandor",
  "summary": "Aboard an Imperial vessel, the captured New Republic Marine and Imperial defector Sandor Woden sits drugged with the truth serum Bavo Six, guarded by Sergeant Tanis, the Mandalorian Master Sergeant Cantrell, and the stormtrooper TK-4792. ISB interrogation specialist Corporal Korynn Fleming arrives on Grand Admiral Kreldin's orders to question Sandor, particularly about a Jedi named Ai'kani. Fleming methodically works the suggestible prisoner, stripping him of his Republic uniform and pressing him to break, but when Ai'kani's name is raised Sandor's defiance flares and he lunges, landing a punch on Fleming's face before Cantrell knocks him unconscious with a rifle butt. Recognizing the strong emotional reaction, Fleming reports to Kreldin in his office that Sandor's defection followed his contact with Ai'kani in custody, suggesting a deep bond. Kreldin resolves to use Sandor as bait, ordering Fleming to send word to the Jedi that she must come to him to retrieve Woden, confident the Jedi's compassion will draw her into the trap.",
